      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal equivalency mapping between validation experiment inputs and COU inputs is not required at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Qualitative similarity between validation and intended-use input parameters has been noted in the validation report. A formal quantitative equivalency analysis is not required at MRL 2 and was not performed."
