    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors achieved their required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at Gradation 1 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 for a Class II device at this model risk level. The CFD hemolysis model is judged credible for identifying worst-case operating conditions in the intended CPB application. This model has been applied in clinical research supporting regulatory submissions and the overall evidence package supports an Accepted decision.",
